<div id="subtree-container" class="subtree-container"><div class="aea2d7dde423afa7ad9351a0886150a8-scss b51b00c1669ad99a1c607cd1e77c2824-scss" style="inset: 0px 269px 617px 0px; justify-content: flex-end;"><div class="afeebf1df237d4103108ba40799802d6-scss b174ef864cda601f37d52e9ca06b1dc7-scss"><div class="c13443431e58facf06f9d12490b92a82-scss" style="width: 90vw; max-width: 8.5in;"><div class="_0df5ec6b9902d7d22ccfa3ebb4f35211-scss">Energy Analysis</div><div class="e5e059a27f4c194020f0d961a3cb5989-scss" dir="auto"><div class="fr-view"><p><span class="fr-img-caption fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil fr-rounded fr-shadow" style="width: 150px;"><span class="fr-img-wrap"><img src="https://localweb-private.lodplanner.com/projects/4/plan-content/18d4c45d-3084-4108-b112-6140c7a17747-BIM%20Use%20Image%20-%20Energy%20Analysis.JPG?Expires=1768815902&amp;Signature=FI~DhZykT16uzkOF0~pxeG6nhvAtROYv2g7BEUb~ECBYYIXn-HTtLPnGDboZOOXRh8-LQESH0kx8EUuQ0KkS3-YnZNT34pUPHR~mVq5wwCWvazMO8bgZxt8tApEEZcvsK4vloB3-kDBPWCKOVDRPMbtX0mApT3QadteGKUxO3KbnVL0HqzGV~GjGsyP0HzGCzNY~mMK2xRuSqRjRunjAWlAaNYoAnliG6lSEdax-fCtuhvuNOkGq0BOAn4vjuRlSLD4v4VEbJ53Y4O0xvdz3pGeIMKIu0DRGPPLzFKa3PRXJ~eJoui4eN1StXEOTm2SYMMW-brLhuOWt3n2L2~0MhQ__&amp;Key-Pair-Id=APKAJRIVA6WNZT4BZJPQ"><span class="fr-inner">Energy Analysis</span></span></span>The BIM Use of Facility Energy Analysis is a process in the facility design phase which one or more building energy simulation programs use a properly adjusted BIM model to conduct energy assessments for the current building design.</p>
<p>The core goal of this BIM use is to inspect building energy standard compatibility and seek opportunities to optimize proposed design to reduce structure's life-cycle costs.</p>
<p><br></p>
<table style="width: 100%;"><thead><tr><th><div style="text-align: left;">Potential Value:&nbsp;</div></th></tr></thead></table>
<ul>
<li>Save time and costs by obtaining building and system information automatically from BIM model instead of inputting data manually</li>
<li>Improve building energy prediction accuracy by auto-determining building information such as geometries, volumes precisely from BIM model</li>
<li>Help with building energy code verification</li>
<li>Optimize building design for better building performance efficiency and reduce building life-cycle cost</li>
</ul>
<table style="width: 100%;"><thead><tr><th><div style="text-align: left;">Resources Required:</div></th></tr></thead></table>
<ul>
<li>Energy analysis tools and software</li>
<li>Knowledge of basic building energy systems</li>
<li>Knowledge of compatible building energy standard</li>
<li>Knowledge and experience of building system design</li>
<li>Ability to manipulate, navigate, and review a 3D Model</li>
<li>Ability to assess a model through engineering analysis tools</li>
</ul>
<table style="width: 100%;"><thead><tr><th><div style="text-align: left;">Team Competencies Required:</div></th></tr></thead></table>
<ul>
<li>Ability to manipulate, navigate, and review a 3D Model</li>
<li>Ability to assess a model through engineering analysis tools</li>
<li>Knowledge of construction means and methods</li>
<li>Design and construction experience</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div></div></div>